Author: CloudySideDown
Text: I have an IUD. No periods if I starve or if I dont. It's kinda great

Author: HappierHungry
Text: tw: numbers    tbh one of my relapse triggers is wanting to lose my period again; not having it for ~1.5yrs and then it being light (for me) and irregular for an additional 2yrs was pretty great, not gonna lie.  ironically, I'm more anaemic now (BMI ~18-19) than I was at my LW (BMI ~15), because my periods are so damn heavy.
